frus:attachment.head:
The Soviet Minister for Foreign Affairs (
    Molotov
) to the British Secretary of State for Foreign
    Affairs (
    Bevin
)A copy of this letter was sent to
    the Secretary of State by Foreign Minister Molotov on October 1, 1946;
    see the Secretary’s letter of November 5, 1946, to Molotov, p. 1015.
